{"tid":2192754,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"受託代理案件遭五毛圍攻  律師助12偷渡港青 內地司法局施壓","createTime":"2020-09-07T10:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T10:22:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3f0ae3599a1160b4bbf89775341f11bff1542c4c","tid":2192754,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:22:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/MWO7DOZ4BRGOJETIOBJYRA52NA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FMWO7DOZ4BRGOJETIOBJYRA52NA%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp1DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=8dc498e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FMWO7DOZ4BRGOJETIOBJYRA52NA%2F&h=c45c6c1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/MWO7DOZ4BRGOJETIOBJYRA52NA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n受託代理案件遭五毛圍攻 <br />\n律師助12偷渡港青 內地司法局施壓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】12名計劃潛逃台灣的港青上月被內地海警截獲，至今扣押於深圳。受家屬委託代理案件的內地律師盧思位昨接受香港傳媒訪問後，隨即在微博遭網民圍剿，被罵「曱甴」、「騙子律師」。盧思位昨向本報表示未料到會被五毛圍攻，但因審查亦不能在微博反駁，「他們可以隨便辱罵我，我要回覆卻發不出去，說起都是一把淚！」他又透露日前收到司法部門來電，要求他就本案備案，「說白了，他們覺得這案重大敏感」；據了解亦有其他代表偷渡港青的律師收到同樣要求。<br />\n<br />\n盧思位上周五嘗試到鹽田看守所會見本案當事人，但情況與內地不少政治案件一樣，盧幾經爭取和投訴後均被拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JK3HHWlCg-1Pkt2VucvAMvzuFtA=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JVKTWXRLSZFG5CHLLYPAJVIWY4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJK3HHWlCg-1Pkt2VucvAMvzuFtA%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJVKTWXRLSZFG5CHLLYPAJVIWY4.jpg&h=360b5162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■前日盧思位到看守所要求與還柙港青會面不果後受訪。 有線電視畫面<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n致電要求備案<br />\n<br />\n盧返回四川後更收到一通司法局的來電，要求他就本案備案，「他打電話過來問我是不是接了一個深圳的偷渡案。我說是，他。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他稱當局實際上對備案沒有一個明確標準，「在管理體系裏面也沒有這。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n對於被大量五毛圍攻，盧稱此前接過其他更加敏感的案件，但都沒有碰到。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鹽田看守所禁會面<br />\n<br />\n在內地代理敏感案，可能會遇上不同「麻煩」，盧思位稱沒想那麼多，。。。。<br />\n<br />\n47歲的盧思位為四川律師，近年代理過成都八九六四酒案，。。。。<br />\n<br />\n12名港人現被刑事拘留在鹽田看守所，近日陸續有收到家屬委託的律師，。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WDgDIC2202xxflaxMblmpNivaKw=/780x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Y4OIQJMWCNFEFLTTLTZ66E5UEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWDgDIC2202xxflaxMblmpNivaKw%3D%2F780x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FY4OIQJMWCNFEFLTTLTZ66E5UEQ.jpg&h=0cb843ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■盧思位昨遭大量五毛在微博圍攻，被罵「與港毒勾結」。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7mBoGGwD7juuS4XHdvtkdBQpBSg=/712x786/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WHWQD77L4RC5HCFJ3QPE6373MA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7mBoGGwD7juuS4XHdvtkdBQpBSg%3D%2F712x786%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWHWQD77L4RC5HCFJ3QPE6373MA.jpg&h=a8cbf5ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n盧思位昨遭大量五毛在微博圍攻，被罵「與港毒勾結」。互聯網"}]}